{
  "stem": "21550.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a good time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, she used to get a little help once in a while, not on a steady basis but--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was very little contact with non-Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] As a matter of fact, the only time we had contact with them is when they beat us up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Especially after we had a game and we happened to be the winners, [LAUGHS] it was very hard to leave the stadium.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before Hitler, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is just in general they would do this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a-- I remember a specific boy, Jan Rutkowski, every time he saw me I had to give him a dime.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He would probably beat me up, because he was stronger than I was and-- but I had rather pay him the dime and-- and have peace.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know where he lived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't-- I wasn't really interested.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, there were specific areas where-- where the Jewish inhabitants were about 90% of the population in those sections.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but we were spread all over the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our neighborhood was, I should say, mostly Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Except in the late '30s when the German propaganda was very strong and it didn't take much to entice the-- the Poles with anti-Semitism, because they-- they're very prone to it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- they used to come, students, university students, on-- in big groups and start trouble in the Jewish section.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to fight back, and we did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we will-- since the Jews were a majority there, we chased them out, and they wouldn't-- they wouldn't  come back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, this was in the late '30s.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Bar mitzvah was not a very big occasion like it's lately here in the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
